title: How Tom Scott Makes Videos
description:
Tom Scott comes to the studio to talk with Marques and Andrew about everything from YouTube Shorts to sky diving! Plus, he shows us how fast he can type the alphabet. Spoiler alert: it's fast. Thanks so much to Tom for coming by to chat and make sure to check out his channels linked below!
